name: Christmas Card.
description:
In May 2021 I joined this NFTs journey. I never imagined that by the end of the year more than 100 people would have loved and collected my works.

You were one of those people. From the bottom of my heart my thanks. I wish you a merry christmas and a happy new year.

I promise I will continue here, building weird things for your enjoyment!

Thank you so much!
________________________________________________________
Note: Don't forget to press/click the Christmas Tree!!!!
